{
  "stem": "5810.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were once-- when I said Buchenwald at the beginning-- we were once looked and, and, and found by an American soldier that said that he had a message for us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had liberated one of the concentration camps, turned out to be Buchenwald, as I remember it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And said-- this is all to my mother, so I am trying to remember because it just doesn't make any sense anymore to me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And due to the fact that I said that, I think males went to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were no females at Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that he had seen a brother and her sister with our name that died the day of liberation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I don't know if that's real.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know if that's true, but based on the fact that I'm told that there were no females in Buchenwald, I'm beginning to wonder if I-- if I know what's right or wrong.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All I know is they've never come back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I've never gotten a death certificate, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In fact, I still have the Red Cross searching today with the, the discovery of new names with the Russian government now releasing a lot of those things.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And hopefully, someday I'll be able to, to know where they died and how they died.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "No one came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And for three years, my mother did that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What we were going to do at that point-- my sister did come back, by the way, from the convents.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And as many hidden children are not doing still till today, we never, never spoke about our experiences, mine at the Barniche.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I only know this today, and I'm, I'm still-- I'm amazed myself that we never spoke about it.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
